\n2323 7716<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hottoyssecretbase/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhottoyssecretbase%2F&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=2509ed77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hottoyssecretbase/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hottoys.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hottoys.com.hk%2F&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=3e90b602\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hottoys.com.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">墮坑前請先睇下自己銀包<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夠錢唔好諗 即刻訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HOT TOYS 原價表 COPY FROM FACEBOOK &quot;Hottoys 香港交流區&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊既都好詳盡，新既話睇下面呢三張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/fsRVRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfsRVRm&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=66456482\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/fsRVRm</a></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCOPY FROM FACEBOOK &lsquo;One Sixth Republic - &lrm;J&uuml;rgen Schulz&lrm;&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNBMb5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNBMb5p.jpg&h=ec3ee46d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2vAPR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2vAPR6.jpg&h=eb901e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WK70gw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWK70gw8.jpg&h=f43696c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79b6db10dbb5f9631252c03bfe0b8310ef1e602f","tid":1326373,"uid":30936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"咁快又爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e077b05ae063ccb7aef75fd3bb3fa538341797","tid":1326373,"uid":117762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q&amp;A</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝 後追丁 巴打提供Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvxR6s4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvxR6s4.jpg&h=163c532c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTBb6s5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTBb6s5.jpg&h=a0de8b02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5FTAmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5FTAmr.jpg&h=ac95c5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZ0MaUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZ0MaUN.jpg&h=5be8f0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 交收個陣有乜要注意呀 好驚有問題呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : IM系列最緊要CHECK下齊唔齊件(參考 威威夏威夷 巴打), 如果店主話自己只CHECK件無玩過正常IM上面都有層膠. 最緊要試埋關節正唔正常 (正常手腳唔會軟手軟腳好似你條賓周咁)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交收訂單要注意最好上去加名,小心比人用報失拎左你件野. 加左名既話就算佢要報失都要兩個人一齊上去先拎到貨 同埋一定要KEEP買賣既RECORD.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>收左單而又驚報失既話可以注意一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（感謝 我現時肯做飯 巴打提供）</strong> </div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：幾錢訂呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：FACEBOOK咪有講囉問問問屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 點解我上網睇隻iron man會咁平 46賣1000幾我係咪執到好野 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你就要睇清楚你個隻係咪powerpose ,pps既價錢同盒都同⅙唔同，一般都平過⅙好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據9巴提供<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1/4 無合金<br />\n<br />\n1/6 會有膠版<br />\n<br />\ndiecast即係合金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(1-7合金暫時出左mk2 3 4 5 6 ,42打後都係合金)<br />\n<br />\npps(42 46 47 hb2.0)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再次鳴謝 9_Januzaj巴打提供<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :想知道ht係咪同款通常唔會再開訂?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係 截左就無得訂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :截左訂點算?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :只可以等現貨(好大機會無)或同其他人收(E.g:facebook group, Yahoo Bid)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n20樓係訂同派貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2樓 Toyhunter就散死貨同少量正野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :幾時截訂? 一個人每次可以訂幾多隻？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :一個人每次只可以訂一隻，唔知幾時截訂 截訂就多數2個月之後 每隻唔同<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想食炒價就訂定 慢慢等 PS:衡量自己財政<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :啲手好難換 點算?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :吹風筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :邊隻邊隻炒唔炒得起?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :關你鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有愛就訂 考慮緊嘅就睇多幾次套戲 唔係唔訂下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :點樣可以保養隻HOT TOYS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 以下轉自網上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要被太陽長時間直射<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n合金長時間在太陽下爆曬，高溫會導致顏色變淺，表面油漆可能會起泡及龜烈，嚴重影響figures的外觀。要留意，就算放到飾櫃但長時間用射燈照視，都可能會導致上述問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n避免在雙手不乾淨時觸碰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手上的汗水與油份很容易黏在合金表面，久而久之就會氧化成一層白白的薄膜，所以接觸figures前最好先將雙手清潔乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意溫度及濕度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港天氣潮濕，所以要十分留意家中的濕度，因為太潮濕會引致生銹;至於溫度方面，太大的溫差會導致熱漲冷縮，令hot toys變得脆弱。所以將空間保持乾爽對保存hot Toys很重要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放入玻璃櫃display , 得閒用除塵帚 掃幾下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIM電池保養方法：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nim果d版電仔唔好長時間放係本體入面<br />\n<br />\n玩完 着完燈 j完好拎哂d電出黎<br />\n<br />\n因為d版電仔放係本體入面耐左會發漲<br />\n<br />\n最後會爆漿 會損壞im d電路<br />\n<br />\n大家玩im開心之餘記得留意下電池咩情況 （BY 舒洛特 巴打）"},{"pid":"92956c346eb6115947595238ce97c068ec9c889e","tid